description.value: Glazed composition amulet of Bastet: represented completely in cat form, modeled in bright blue glazed composition with dark speckles on her coat; there is a suspension loop behind her neck. As goddess of fertility her kittens provide proof of her fecundity: she is attended by no less than ten of them. One sits on top of her head, another lies on her back, six sit supporting her outstretched forelegs on their heads and two more balance on the forelegs.
